         generate_adapter_arm ─────→ mi-adapters-template.json
                                      │
Phase 4: package_site ────────────→ PackageResults.json + site ZIPs
         generate_migration_settings → MigrationSettings.json
                                      │
Phase 5: confirm_migration ◄──────────┘
